project_descr: While women make up over half of the population and provide significant contribution to society, a disparity remains in terms of the fulfillment of their needs and the services and protections afforded to them by the government.

outputs.output_descr: There is a need to come up with broader UNDP programme that strengthens women’s rights in the Philippines. Two opportunities will be launched to ensure fulfillment of its objective to empower women:

project_title: strengthening women’s rights in the philippines
